<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Question Reply</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Your Question Has Been Answered</h2>
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Your question regarding the course <strong><%= title %></strong> has been answered. 
          <!-- Here is the response:</p>
        <blockquote>
            <%= answer %>
        </blockquote> -->
        <p>Please login to view the reply .If you have any further questions, please feel free to ask.</p>
        <!-- <a href="<%= courseLink %>" class="button">View Course</a> -->
        <p>Thank you,</p>
        <p>The Course Support Team</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
